Remix of Tiny Biggest Tank Classic Double Barrel Tank Hunter by the talented woddish.
Changed the main canon and sponson weapons.

Summary from the creator :

Tiny tanks! The perfect thing to give a sense of scale to your tiny titans, tiny aircraft, or tiny anything! Add them as base decoration, add them as terrain decoration, create tiny war dioramas, do whatever you want with them! Anything is made better with the addition of tiny tanks.

This tiny tank has been a long (long long) time coming. Regretfully the tiny manufactorum fell behind, got caught up, couldn't get the mojo flowing, but now the long wait is over.
Presenting, twin barrels of fun for all your tiny titan hunting needs! This baby won't cook your tiny foes like the tiny portable microwave, but it will punch two holes straight through them. And I don't think tiny titans sound like much of a threat when they're suddenly missing key parts of their tiny robotic bodies.

Tiny tanks are intended for resin printers.
